OL,3,CJersey's government publishes redacted
OL,4,CDFDS ferry contract
OL,6,FWatch: ITV Channel's Emma Volney
OL,7,Funpicks the contract
OL,9,FJersey's government has revealed, for
OL,10,Fthe first time, the contents of the 20-
OL,11,Fyear contract it has signed with
OL,12,FDanish ferry operator DFDS.
OL,14,FThe release follows huge pressure from
OL,15,Fislanders calling for greater
OL,16,Ftransparency over what has - and
OL,17,Fhasn't - been agreed to.
