OL,3,CJersey's government publishes redacted
OL,4,CDFDS ferry contract
OL,6,FUnder the agreement, DFDS is granted
OL,7,Fexclusive access to the Elizabeth
OL,8,FTerminal ramps and is obliged to
OL,9,Fintroduce new, greener ships. The
OL,10,Fcontract also includes termination
OL,11,Fclauses and sets out terms covering
OL,12,Fmaximum fares and staffing
OL,13,Farrangements.
