OL,3,CJersey's government publishes redacted
OL,4,CDFDS ferry contract
OL,6,FIt further outlines the rationale
OL,7,Fbehind the new "flat-rate" freight
OL,8,Fcharging structure for businesses,
OL,9,Fwhich is intended to create a more
OL,10,Flevel playing field, but has been
OL,11,Fsubject to criticism from retailers no
OL,12,Flonger able to negotiate their own
OL,13,Fdeals.
OL,15,FJersey's Economic Development
OL,16,FMinister, Deputy Kirsten Morel, said:
OL,17,F"We are now in a situation where we
OL,18,Fhave a ferry service that is price-
OL,19,Fprotected" and attributed business
OL,20,Fconcerns to the impact of UK food
OL,21,Finflation on local prices.
