OL,4,CDFDS ferry contract
OL,6,FHowever, he added that if revenues
OL,7,Ffall drastically short of expectations
OL,8,Fand investment is at serious risk,
OL,9,FDFDS could raise fares above inflation
OL,10,F- but only following extensive
OL,11,Fengagement and prior approval from
OL,12,Fgovernment officials.
OL,14,FWhat the contract does not include is
OL,15,Fany requirement for DFDS to operate
OL,16,Ffast sailings during the winter months
OL,17,For to provide inter-island services
OL,18,Fbetween Jersey and Guernsey.
