OL,6,FDeputy Morel added: "It wasn't
OL,7,Fpossible - we had no access to
OL,8,FGuernsey's port and no way to contract
OL,9,Fa party to another port like that."
OL,11,FJersey's Chamber of Commerce has
OL,12,Fwelcomed the publication of the Ferry
OL,13,FConcession Agreement between the
OL,14,FGovernment of Jersey and DFDS, noting
OL,15,Fthat this release 'brings long-sought
OL,16,Fclarity to the terms governing the
OL,17,Fisland's essential sea connectivity'.
