OL,6,FChamber has consistently called for
OL,7,Fgreater transparency around the
OL,8,Fobligations and expectations set out
OL,9,Fin the operating framework for ferry
OL,10,Fservices.
OL,12,FIt said: "The publication of this
OL,13,Fdetailed 132-page agreement and
OL,14,Fexplanatory note is therefore a
OL,15,Fpositive step towards that goal."
