OL,3,CJersey's government publishes redacted
OL,4,CDFDS ferry contract
OL,6,FLee Madden, President of the Jersey
OL,7,FChamber of Commerce, said: "Whilst the
OL,8,Ffuller detail of the 132 pages will
OL,9,Frequire closer examination, we are
OL,10,Fpleased that our calls for better
OL,11,Funderstanding of what is required of
OL,12,Fthe ferry operator have been met.
OL,14,FChamber also understands from
OL,15,Fengagement with its members that there
OL,16,Fhas now been a reversal of the
OL,17,Fdecision to apply extra freight
OL,18,Fcharges.
