OL,3,CJersey's government publishes redacted
OL,4,CDFDS ferry contract
OL,6,FJersey Chamber of Commerce CEO, Murray
OL,7,FNorton, said: "In late July, Chamber
OL,8,Fbecame aware of additional charges
OL,9,Fbeing applied alongside the newly
OL,10,Fintroduced flat-rate freight pricing.
OL,12,FThese charges would have added #135.38
OL,13,Fto each trailer of freight and several
OL,14,Fmillion pounds to the annual cost of
OL,15,Ffreight. It was also planned that the
OL,16,Fferry operator would retrospectively
OL,17,Fapply these additional port dues
OL,18,Fcharges to customers.
