OL,3,CJersey's government publishes redacted
OL,4,CDFDS ferry contract
OL,6,FFollowing a joint review of the port
OL,7,Fcharging framework, Chamber now
OL,8,Funderstands that DFDS will limit the
OL,9,Fapplication of port dues to a per-
OL,10,Ftonne basis only and will not pass on
OL,11,Fthe per-unit charges previously
OL,12,Fcommunicated. In line with this
OL,13,Fclarification, DFDS will remove the
OL,14,Fper-unit charge from freight invoices
OL,15,Fwith immediate effect.
